Investor Holland Says Stocks May Face ‘Melt-Up’ (Audio)

-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-20T12:37:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/investor-holland-says-stocks-may-face-melt-up-audio-.html
Michael Holland , chairman of Holland
& Co., says the number of short positions in the stock market is
so high that "we could get a stock melt-up." Holland talks with 
Bloomberg's Ken Prewitt and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 15:38
 